$PAR
$HR
$PAR
True or false:
If \(f \colon {\mathbb{R}} \to \mathbb{R}\) and
\(g \colon {\mathbb{R}} \to \mathbb{R}\) are differentiable functions
(differentiable at all points), then \(h := f+g\) (defined by the pointwise
sum) is differentiable.
$BR
END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

$q4 = RadioButtons([
"True",
