BEGIN_TEXT
\{ $q4->buttons \}

$PAR
True or false:
If \(f \colon {\mathbb{R}} \to \mathbb{R}\) and
\(g \colon {\mathbb{R}} \to \mathbb{R}\) are functions and
\(h := f+g\) is differentiable, then \(f\) and \(g\) are differentiable.
$BR
END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

$q5 = RadioButtons([
"True",
"False",
],
"False",
